If a DropdownButtonFormField menu item is selected after selecting a text field, the focus returns to the text field. This is similar to https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/47128, which was closed and marked as fixed after https://github.com/flutter/flutter/pull/93716, but the issue is still appearing with DropdownButtonFormField. 

## Steps to Reproduce

<!-- Please include full steps to reproduce so that we can reproduce the problem. -->

1. Execute `flutter run` on the code sample <!-- (see "Code sample" section below) -->
2. Tap on the text field
3. Tap on the dropdown menu and select something from it

**Expected results:**
Focus should stay on the DropdownButtonFormField. 

**Actual results:** 
Focus returned to the TextFormField, popping up the keyboard (and, in a larger application, scrolling the screen back up or down to the TextFormField). 

